hadiths[18]{hadithnumber,text}:
3718,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu)) ney farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bethey they ke aap key paas qabila Hawazin ka wafad hazir huwa aur unhoney kaha : aey Muhammad ! hum eik asal Arbi qabila hain aur hum par jo musibat nazil hui hai aap us sey ba-khoobi waqif hain, lihaza aap hum par ehsan farmaain , Allah Taala aap par ehsan farmaey. aap ney farmaya : tum maal lena pasand kar lo ya apni aurten aur apney bachchey. wo kehney lagey : aap ney hamein maal aur khandan mein sey eik chiz pasand karney ko farmaya hai to hum apni aurton aur apney bachchon ko pasand kartey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo merey aur Abdul-Muttalib key khandan key hissey mein aaye hain, wo mainey tumhen dey diye. jab main Zohar ki namaz sey farigh houn to tum khadey ho kar kehna : hum momineen sey apney biwi bachey wapis leney key liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey madad chaahney wale hain. jab logon ney Zohar ki namaz padh li to unhoney khadey ho kar yehi baat kahi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo merey aur Abdul-Muttalib key khandan key hissey mein aaya hai, wo to tumhara ho gaya. muhajrin kehney lagey : jo hamarey hissey mein aaye hain unka ikhtiyar bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko hai. ansaar ney bhi kaha : jo kuchh hamarey hissey mein aaya hai, us ka ikhtiyar bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko hai. Aqra bin Habis ney kaha : main aur banu Tameem to kisi ko ikhtiyar nahin detey. Uena bin Hisn ney kaha : main aur (mera qabeela) Banu Fazara bhi apney hissey mein kisi ko ikhtiyar nahin detey. Abbas bin Mirdas us ney kaha : main aur (mera qabeela) banu Sulaim bhi ikhtiyar nahin detey. banu Sulaim uth khadey huye aur kehney lagey : to ghalat kehta hai. jo kuchh hamarey hissey mein aaya hai us ka ikhtiyar bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey logo ! inhen in ki aurten aur bachchey wapis kar do. albatta jo shakhs is ghanimat sey apney hissey ko barqarar rakhna chahey to usey (is hissey key iwaz) chhe-chhe oont mil jaeyngey, us maal mein sey jo pehley pehal Allah hamein ata farmaeyga (lekin ab wo apna hissa chhod dey). phir aap apni oontni par sawar huye to log bhi sawar huye (aur aap ko gherey mein ley liya ) ke hamein ghanimat taqseem kar dijiye yahan tak ke unhoney is dhakam-pail mein aap ko eik darkht tak pahuncha diya. aap ki chadar darkht key kaanton mein phans gaee. aap ney farmaya : aey logo ! mujhey meri chadar to wapis kar do. Allah ki qism ! agar tumharey liye (merey paas) tahaama key darakhton key barabar oont hotey to main wo sab tum mein taqseem kar deta, phir tum mujhey bakheel (kanjus) ya buzdil ya jhoota na paatey. phir aap eik oont key paas aaye. uskey kohaan sey kuchh oon ukhaadi aur apni do ungliyon ke darmiyan pakad kar irshad farmaya : suno ! aey logo ! merey liye maale-fai mein sey kuchh bhi nahin, itna bhi nahin, ilawa khums (paanchwen hissey) key aur wo bhi wapis tumhen hi mil jata hai. (ye sun kar) eik aadmi baalon ka eik guchchaa ley kar utha aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey apney oont ka nameeda durust karney key liye ye guchchaa liya tha. aap ney farmaya : is mein jo to mera aur Abdul-Muttalib key khandan ka hissa tha wo tujhey maaf hai (baqi ko to janey). wo shakhs kehney laga : is maamuli si chiz ka ye martaba hai? mujhey iski koi zarurat nahin aur us ney usey phenk diya. aap ney farmaya : aey logo ! sooi aur dhaagey tak (maale-ghanimat) merey paas pahuncha do kyonkey khayanat qiyamat key din khayanat karney waley key liye aeb aur aar (sharm) ban jaeygi."
3719,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs hiba kar key wapis nahin ley sakta magar walid apni aulad sey wapis ley sakta hai. aur hiba kar key wapis leney wala us kuttey ki tarah hai jo qai kar key phir chaat'ta hai.
3720,"Hazrat ibne-Umar aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi ko Atiya dey to phir uskey liye jayez nahin ke usey wapis ley magar walid apni aulad ko jo Atiya dey, usey wapis ley sakta hai. aur jo shakhs tohfa dey kar wapis leta hai, wo kuttey ki tarah hai jo khata hai yahan tak ke jab zarurat sey ziyada sair ho jata hai to qai karta hai, phir apni qai ko chaatney lagta hai."
3721,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hiba kar key wapis leney wala kuttey ki tarah hai jo qai karta hai, phir apni qai chaatney lagta hai."
3722,"Hazrat Taoos sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi key liye jayez nahin ke koi chiz hiba kerey. phir usey wapis ley. magar baap apni aulad sey wapis ley sakta hai. Hazrat Taoos ney kaha : jab main bacha tha to main suna karta tha ke padhi. qai chaatney wala padhi. lekin us waqt mujhey ye ilm nahin tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aisey shakhs ki misal bayan ki hai aur farmaya : jo shakhs aisey kerey. uski misal kuttey ki tarah hai jo khata hai, phir qai karta hai, phir apni qai chaatta hai."
3723,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs sadqa (ya tohfa ) dey kar wapis leta hai, wo kuttey ki tarah hai jo apni qai mein lot jata hai, yani usey kha leta hai."
3724,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs sadqa kar key wapis leta hai, uski misal kuttey ki tarah hai jo qai kar key is mein lot jata hai, yani usey chaatney lagta hai."
3725,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs sadqa kar key usey wapis ley leta hai, uski misal kuttey ki tarah hai jo qai kar key usey chaatta hai. Imam Auzai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain : mainey Muhammad bin Ali bin Husein sey suna, wo ye hadees Ata bin abi ribaah ko bayan kar rahey they."
3726,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hiba kar key ruju karney wala apni qai chaatney waley ki tarah hai.
3727,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tohfey mein ruju karney wala apni qai qai chaatney waley ki tarah hai.
3728,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamen buri misal ka misdaaq nahin banna chahiye. tohfa dey kar wapis leney wala apni qai chaatney waley ( kuttey ) ki tarah hai.
3729,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hum par buri misal saadiq nahin aani chahiye. hiba kar key ruju karney wala kuttey ki tarah hai jo apni qai chaatta hai.
3730,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : buri misal hamarey liye munasib nahin. hiba wapis leney waley ki misal kuttey aur uski qai jaisi hai."
3731,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tohfa dey kar wapis leney wala kuttey ki tarah hai jo qai karta hai, phir us qai ko chatna shuru kar deta hai."
3732,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hiba kar key wapis leney wala apni qai chaatney waley ( kuttey ) ki tarah hai.
3733,"Hazrat ibne-Umar aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi shakhs key liye halal nahin ke wo Atiya dey kar wapis ley magar walid apni aulad ko Atiya dey kar wapis ley sakta hai. aur jo shakhs Atiya dey kar wapis leta hai, wo us kuttey ki tarah hai jo khata hai yahan tak ke jab ( zarurat sey ziyada) sair ho jata hai to qai kar deta hai, phir dobara usey chatna shuru kar deta hai."
3734,"Hazrat Taoos (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi key liye jayez nahin ke wo tohfa dey kar ruju kerey. albatta walid kar sakta hai. Hazrat Taoos ney kaha : main bachon ko yun kehtey sunta tha, wo keh rahey hotey : O apni qai chaatney waley ! lekin mujhey ye ilm nahin tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey bator misal bayan farmaya hai yahan tak ke mujhey ye hadees pahunchi : jo shakhs hiba kar key wapis ley, uski misal kuttey jaisi hai jo apni qai chaatta hai."
3735,"Hazrat Taoos (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hamen aisi shakhsiyat ney bataya jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki ziyaarat farmaai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs hiba kar key ruju karta hai, uski misal us kuttey jaisi hai jo khata hai, phir qai karta hai, phir apni qai chaatta hai."
